data.description: Your new home awaits!!! Don't miss your chance to own this charming home in lemoore with an amazing porch, open floor plan and plenty of room for entertaining. Enjoy the cool summer evenings on the porch and then warm up in the built in spa. This home includes artificial grass for minimal yard maintenance and includes multiple outdoor fireplaces to keep you warm on those coldnights. Run don't walk and schedule your private showing today.
